interpretation:
The "person walking" card signifies forward movement and progress. It represents a desire to move forward and take action towards your goals. This card can indicate independence and the need for self-motivation to achieve your desired outcome. It may also suggest a need to break away from the status quo and forge your own path.

This card can symbolize physical movement, such as travel or a change of scenery. It can also represent emotional or mental movement, such as making progress in personal growth or overcoming obstacles. This card reminds us that sometimes progress requires taking the first step, even if it feels uncomfortable or unfamiliar.

Overall, the "person walking" card encourages us to embrace change and take action towards our desired outcome, whether it be through physical, emotional, or mental movement. It reminds us that progress is possible with determination and a willingness to take risks.
